<B>__{series of cuts}
<A>__{as the train continues its eastward journey... samuel stares raptly out of the window at the changing patterns of the countryside. he points in wonder at a brightly colored hot air balloon as it drifts slowly over timbered hills... he looks unsure as the pattern of field and wood gives way to suburbs, bustling shopping centers, restaurants, car lots and fast food outlets.}
